 ltd news » more t news earnings vs estimates » more financials related topics stocksstock screenermarket dataadvertising  marketing ruder finn  wikipedia ruder finn from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from kyodo public relations jump to navigation search ruder finn type private industry communications public relations marketing founded  headquarters new york city beijing area served global key people kathy bloomgarden ceo david finn founder bill ruder founder website wwwruderfinncom ruder finn is a public relations with coheadquarters in the united states and china it is one of the world’s largest privately owned communications agencies the agency has four divisions health  wellness corporate reputation  transformation rfi studios and consumer connections contents  history  clients  references  external links historyedit ruder finn was established in  in new york by david finn and bill ruder their first client was perry comocitation needed and over time they expanded their network to include consumer products companies as well as government agencies in the s through late s while representing longtime client philip morris now altria ruder finn was instrumental in crafting the public relations campaign that disputed the evidence tobacco smoking is hazardous to health in  ruder finn ran the global climate coalition a group of mainly united states businesses opposing action to reduce greenhouse gas emissions in  the firm was caught in a conflict of interest after it was revealed that it represented both the jewish agency for israel and switzerland government the jewish agencys world jewish restitution organization was pursuing a settlement with the swiss government over its financial dealings during world war ii in  ruder finn established rfi studios a digital practice to help clients protect and build their reputation online the agency expanded in asia establishing offices in shanghai beijing hong kong guangzhou singapore delhi mumbai and bangalore in  pro bono work done for the un raised speculation when kofi annans nephew kobina worked as an intern at the firm in  ruder finn accepted a contract worth from the government of maldives that was condemned by the commonwealth of nations for organizing a political coup détat that led to the fall of the first democratically elected president of the maldives vicepresident of ruder finn tchividjian admitted there were diverse points of views surrounding the circumstances around the change of government the commonwealth ministerial action group reiterated its call for early elections to be held in the maldives in  ruder finn acquired thunder communications a chinese event management brand and marketing consultancy and formed a partnership with kyodo public relations the agency has won the prsa bronze anvils big apple awards sabres and prweek awards david finn received a big apple award in april  the firm paid  million for a squarefoot property on east rd street for new corporate headquarters for the firm in  ruder finn acquired kyodo public relations one of the largest independent pr firms in japan and the first pr agency to be listed on jasdaq securities exchange clientsedit this article is in a list format that may be better presented using prose you can help by converting this article to prose if appropriate editing help is available november  caribou coffee johnson  johnson kraft foods microsoft novartis pepsico pfizer ppr swiss private bankers association tivo tods  referencesedit  httpwwwcnncombusinesskeepingitinthefamilyindexhtml  david finn the way forward my first fifty years at ruder finn new york millwood publishing  p    ruder  finn inc project “b” an alternative proposal to project “a”″ september  tobacco institute bates no timn archived march   at webcite  ruder  finn inc public relations study for philip morris inc january  philip morris bates no  archived march   at webcite  ruder  finn inc preliminary proposal for a corporate affairs programme february  phi