include holding fixed period pr activities as well as pr events to notify the opening of events such as exhibitions and art shows the paid publicity segment helps customers to post their publicity contents on newspaper and magazinesrevenue in jpy ttmbnnet income in jpymincorporatedemployeeslocationkyodo public relations co ltdf dowa bldg  ginzachuoku japanjpnphone fax websitehttpwwwkyodoprcojpmore ▼peer analysiskey informationkey informationstock performanceper share dataefficiencymanagement effectivenessprofitabilityfinancial strengthgrowth ratescompanyrevenue ttmnet income ttmmarket capemployeespriceearnings ttmpricebook value mrqpricecash flow ttmpricesales ttmeps excl extraordinary items ttmeps incl extraordinary items ttmrevenue per share ttmbook value per share mrqasset turnover ttminventory turnover ttmreceivables turnover ttmrevenues per employee ttmreturn on avg assets ttmreturn on avg assets  yr avgreturn on investment ttmreturn on investment  yr avggross margin ttmgross margin yr avgnet profit margin ttmnet profit margin yr avgquick ratio mrqinterest coverage ttmtotal debt to capital mrqpayout ratio yr avgrevenueyoy change revenue yr growth ratenet incomeyoy change net income yr growth ratecapital expenditure yr growth ratedividend yr growth ratecrie anabuki incbnmbnkyodo public relations coltdbnmbnjtec corporationbnmbnsds holdings co ltdbnmbntakase corporationbnmbnharima bstem corporationbnmbnkhirayama holdings co ltdbnmbnktrust holdings incbnmbnyamada servicer synthetic office co ltdbnmbnenvironmental control center co ltdbnmbndata as of aug   currency figures normalised to kyodo public relations co ltds reporting currency japanese yen jpy income statement jpyyear on year kyodo public relations co ltd grew revenues  from bn to bn while net income improved  from m to mft lexiconfor more information visit the ft lexiconlexicon on this pageexplore our toolsalertsdata archiveportfolioworld marketsequities screenerfunds overview  thomson reuters click for re