strategies and the support for emergency management publicity the optional and spot segment provides services for companies based on contracts of less than six months the optional services include holding press conferences press seminars pr events survey publicity as well as websites design and company profiles production the spot services include holding fixed period pr activities as well as pr events to notify the opening of events such as exhibitions and art shows the paid publicity segment helps customers to post their publicity contents on newspaper and magazines » full overview of t company address kyodo public relations co ltd f dowa bldg  ginzachuoku   tky    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation takashi kamimura  yosuke kanno  hideyuki numata  ryoichi shinozaki  masato nishii  » more officers  directors kyodo public relations co ltd news » more t news related topics stocksstock screeneradvertising  marketing kyodo public relations co ltd logout  my account  premium content follow us please refer to our privacy policy for important information on the use of cookies by continuing to use this website you agree to this close charting the future of public relations signup menu latest longreads focus rankings  data events  awards agency playbook latestnewsthe latest pr news from the holmes reportopinionopinion and commentary from the holmes reportpodcaststhe holmes reports echo chamber pr show lifts the lid on key stories and trendsvideoslatest video interviews and campaigns from the holmes reportlongreadspremium contentlongform journalism that analyzes the issues challenges and opportunities facing the business and practice of pranalysisindustryleading analysis of the pr stories that matterprofiles  interviewsup close and personal with leaders from the marketing and pr worldsresearch  trendskeeping up with the latest thinking on pr industry expansion focuscannescoverage of the cannes lions from the holmes report in association wi